Move-in Ready 3 Bed 2 Bath Home With Private in-Law Suite 7,564 sqft Lot / 2,405 home.

As you search for your perfect new home, finding a move-in ready property that checks all the boxes on your wish list can seem an impossible task. However, this recently renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom house with an detached private in-law suite could be the ideal solution for your needs. Located in a quiet, family-friendly neighborhood, this home offers spacious, open-concept living areas, a modern kitchen and bedrooms with ample space. The secluded in-law suite includes a large living space, and full bathroom perfect for elderly parents or adult children in need of independence. With its ideal layout, prime location, and turnkey condition, this desirable residence won’t last long. Act now for your chance to make this house your home.
 
Spacious and Renovated 3 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom Home. This spacious and recently renovated 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home is move-in ready. The open-concept features a living room, dining area, and kitchen with plenty of living space. Tile Floors Throughout Gorgeous tile floors run throughout the entire home providing a warm and welcoming feel. The living room is spacious enough for both sitting and recreational areas making it cozy for entertaining or relaxing. Three Bright Bedrooms and Two Full Bathrooms There are three well-sized bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The master bedroom features an ensuite bathroom for maximum convenience. The two additional bedrooms are on the opposite side of the landing, with a full bathroom close to both.
Bright, Open Concept Kitchen and Living Areas The open concept kitchen and living area is the heart of this home. Recently renovated with quality finishes, it is bright, spacious and ideal for entertaining or quiet nights in. Kitchen The kitchen features wood cabinetry and beautiful countertops
 Spacious Living Room The living room brings in natural light thanks to large windows and opens to the kitchen, creating an airy flow between spaces. This flexible area could be used as a family room, playroom or home office. There are gleaming tile floors throughout for easy cleaning and style.
 Private In-Law Suite A separate entrance leads to a private in-law or guest suite, perfect for live-in help or visiting family. The suite has a large living space, full bathroom, and a large closet. Residents will appreciate the privacy and independence this section of the home affords, an open layout, private in-law suite and move-in ready condition, this bright 3 bed 2 bath home is ideal for a family looking for spaciousness, style and convenience. Schedule a private showing to view this must-see property today
. Conclusion As you can see, this charming and move-in ready home has much to offer for both families and those looking to accommodate extended family or generate rental income. With an open concept main floor, spacious bedrooms, updated bathrooms, and a private in-law suite, there are options for all. The inviting backyard provides an ideal space for relaxing or entertaining, and the home’s location offers proximity to schools, shopping, dining, and outdoor recreation. For those seeking a turnkey property in a peaceful neighborhood, this recently renovated home warrants a closer look. With so many amenities and possibilities packed into an affordable package, homes like this do not come along every day. Act now before another discerning buyer capitalizes on this rare opportunity. Please contact (602)639-1127 for inquiries.
